    preuve
</a>
</td>
                    <td class="stars">★★★☆</td>
                </tr>

                {# AC 11.06 #}
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="badge-ac">AC11.06</span></td>
                    <td>Installer un poste client et expliquer la procédure.</td>
                    <td><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/163DVFQeLOINDI6rUItSrpxgygIfKmrVi/edit?usp=drive_link&ouid=106987235666399691783&rtpof=true&sd=true" target="_blank" class="btn-preuve">
            Preuve
        </a>
